<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Spotify ile Giriş Yap</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .login-container {
            padding: 3rem;
            background-color: var(--background-deep);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 16px;
        }
        .btn-spotify {
            background-color: #1DB954;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 500px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .btn-spotify:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <h1>Portfolyomu Görüntüle</h1>
        <p style="color: #a0a0a0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Müzik zevkimi görmek için lütfen Spotify hesabınızla giriş yapın.</p>
        <a href="/login" class="btn-spotify">
            <i class="fab fa-spotify"></i>
            <span>Spotify ile Giriş Yap</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
